{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ABOUT THIS GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become an almighty <strong>Gladiator</strong> in this fast-paced Action Roguelike <strong>Crystalis Descendant</strong>. The <strong>Crystallisk</strong> are swarming the Arena and are out to destroy the vital <strong>Crystal</strong>. It is up to you to stop them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become stronger each time you face this relentless horde as you unlock newfound powers through their essence. Face the challenges of the <strong>Arena</strong> and uncover what lurks below.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/Steam_PageAssets_Gifs_ProtectCrystal.gif?t=1733216029\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PROTECT THE CRYSTAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>Crystal</strong> is the heart of the <strong>Arena</strong> and the source of your power. Protect it at all costs and reap its rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/Steam_PageAssets_Gifs_ChargingCrystal.gif?t=1733216029\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CHARGE THE CRYSTAL AND UNLEASH ITS POWER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather <strong>Crystal Essence</strong> to charge the <strong>Crystal</strong> and unleash its devastating pulse to eliminate any remaining <strong>Crystallisk</strong> and proceed to unlock even greater powers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/Steam_PageAssets_Gifs_CrystalliskHorde.gif?t=1733216029\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FACE HORDES OF CRYSTALLISK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From raging <strong>Ravagers</strong> to indomitable <strong>Ironscales</strong>. Face a great variety of crystal monsters known as the <strong>Crystallisk</strong>, each with their own attacks and skills. Be prepared to face trials and challenges as they are out to defeat you to get to the <strong>Crystal</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/Steam_PageAssets_Gifs_BreakingPillars.gif?t=1733216029\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>USE YOUR SURROUNDINGS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the <strong>Arena</strong> to your advantage and destroy the environment using it to outsmart the horde by blocking their path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/Steam_PageAssets_Gifs_Shop.gif?t=1733216029\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>UNLEASH POWERFUL UPGRADES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a <strong>Poison</strong> master, gain a thirst for blood or perhaps, become a <strong>Void</strong> fanatic as you unlock new upgrades and fight your way through each wave! Discover you own playstyle with over 80 upgrades and many more to come!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CONQUER THE MUTATIONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You never know what lurks in the depths while descending into the <strong>Arena</strong>. These <strong>Mutations</strong> are giant aberrations which have been roaming underground for aeons and are awaiting to devour new <strong>Gladiators</strong> coming their way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/Steam_PageAssets_Gifs_Dash.gif?t=1733216029\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BECOME AN ALMIGHTY GLADIATOR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be the <strong>Gladiator</strong> that resides within you. Experiment with different builds, unlock new weapons and characters with each their own unique playstyle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FORGE GAME-CHANGING ENHANCEMENTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Return to the <strong>Sanctuary</strong> and use the <strong>Forge</strong> to craft new enhancements for your abilities, weapons, and even the <strong>Crystal</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ROADMAP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover our plans for the future! Take a look at our roadmap to see what exciting updates and content we have in store for <strong>Crystalis Descendant</strong>. We're committed to delivering a thrilling and evolving experience for our players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/CrystalisDescendant_Roadmap2.png?t=1733216029\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some thanks are definitely in order!  We are a small team developing games we love, so we would like to thank you and our amazing community for all the support so far. Without you, we wouldn't be here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733216029","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/page.bg.jpg?t=1733216029","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733216029","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733216029","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":